{"tid":1551473,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家打低一個陳怡有咩用,仲有千千萬萬個","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T15:39:14.000Z","uid":254452,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"48e28a5cb8dd19b9e581b75c859b9cd409b18d45","tid":1551473,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩係youtube睇睇下其他野,就彈左呢條撚樣出黎<br />\n條撚樣扭曲事實,廢話多多,但唔少片都過十萬view, 過萬like<br />\n連登仔之前對付陳怡就好巴閉,但呢條友日日就風流快活講on9野都仲生勾勾繼續賺錢<br />\n比我都唔怕你地。<br />\n<br />\n最過份係呢一段,話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">爆眼女義士好假</span></span>,乜乜柒柒,你唔係仲忍呀?我就忍唔撚到,係咁負皮佢!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sU36GwU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsU36GwU.png&h=fc8284f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpXjg5t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpXjg5t.png&h=3d495f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同之前一樣,我用個懇樣懇求各位,條條片禁入去即pause,然後負皮上一頁,直到收佢皮為止!<br />\n唔好再比佢散播謠言歪理!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HS5g3Lp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHS5g3Lp.png&h=0cd494a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb5e9fb7f73a351e13cb7b397d0b26e91da27969","tid":1551473,"uid":254452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"呢撚樣就叫Simon, 肥柒毒一條,講歪理刷存在感,<br />\n懇求大家一齊比多D存在感佢,不過係負面的,刷到佢懷疑人生!"},{"pid":"99cf61bad0654863b4b3d8566a3f739591dcd594","tid":1551473,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"自推(1/10)"},{"pid":"81a6d76747d9bcc476bcde192410cdb4a69002e9","tid":1551473,"uid":21609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ee00ee72873de1e3476d8640e26b62af0690